    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, true mint-condition vehicle that shows about as well as a used car can. It runs and drives beautifully, feels tight and smooth on the road, and shows only the slightest signs of prior use. The exterior presents extremely well, the interior is very clean and well-kept, and overall this is the kind of vehicle that should impress even picky buyers looking for a top-condition example.",
