    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows age and wear consistent with a well-used car, making it a practical choice for a value-focused buyer, commuter, or project-minded owner. If you're looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overpaying, this is a compelling opportunity.",
