    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right buyer. It\u2019s not winning any beauty contests, but if you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a project, or a useful parts car, this one could make a lot of sense. Priced to be accessible and sold with a friendly, straightforward approach.",
