      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great bones and a drivetrain that still shows good character. Starts, moves, and delivers the kind of analog feel enthusiasts look for, with a responsive engine note, usable torque, and a chassis that feels worth saving. Cosmetically it needs attention and it\u2019s not pretending to be perfect, but for someone wanting an affordable driver/project, this is a straightforward platform with real upside. A smart buy for a hands-on owner who wants something inexpensive, mechanical, and rewarding.",
