    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn personality you can\u2019t fake\u2014an ideal pick for someone who values grit, utility, and the chance to make something their own. It has a bold, broken-in presence and the kind of everyday practicality that still shines through, whether you need a budget-friendly runabout, a project with promise, or a dependable spare to keep life moving. There\u2019s real charm here for the right buyer: a machine with stories behind it and more chapters left to write.",
