      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values practicality, affordability, and a straightforward deal. A solid opportunity for a commuter, first-time driver, or project-minded shopper looking for usable transportation without a big upfront cost.",
