      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with good bones and plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner that could make a great cheap daily, first car, or project for someone handy. It\u2019s priced to reflect the wear and tear, and for the money it offers a lot of value if you want simple, affordable transport without spending a fortune. If you know what you\u2019re looking at, there\u2019s a solid opportunity here.",
